 ## 2026-07-17 Australia/Sydney - ADP V0.1 task ADP-S4-P05-T056 (Coverage Debt + As-of history query base; NOT_DEPLOYED)
 
 - Fifty-sixth task of the ADP V0.1 FINAL EXECUTION program (S4-P05). A Coverage-Debt + As-of history query base over the 2016+ backfilled corpus (the A0 waves T046/T047 and the A1 provinces T050), providing the ground-truth completeness and point-in-time layer the T048 gap gate deferred to. release_mode NOT_DEPLOYED; a query base, the production worker/cron/data untouched. New tool arxiv-daily-push/docs/pursuing_goal/v0_1/tools/coverage_asof.py provides coverage_debt (the full 2016+ window grid per source, every cell classified so every hole is explainable, reusing the T043 gap detector), as_of_query (the version known as of a date, resolved by parsed dates not lexical strings, cross-checked by an independent oracle, reusing the T048-proven resolver), and historical_manifest_resolver (the latest monthly snapshot manifest known as of a date, never a future one). Deliverables under arxiv-daily-push/docs/pursuing_goal/v0_1/evidence/ADP-S4-P05-T056/: coverage_asof_report.json, known_gaps.md, and adversarial_review.md (review CONFIRMED_SOUND; verifier hardened to full live re-derivation). Acceptance verified (evidence/ADP-S4-P05-T056/test-results/base_tests.txt, ACCEPTANCE = PASS, exit 0): 693 revision samples across 21 chains and 33 query dates from 2016 to 2026 resolve with 0 future-version leakage and 0 disagreements against the independent oracle, at or above the 100 target; the coverage grid of 180 cells (5 sources by their 2016+ windows) has 11 covered and 169 debt cells, all explained (139 source-not-yet-active, 30 not-backfilled), with 0 UNEXPLAINED; the as-of guarantee is non-vacuous, since a deliberately broken resolver produces a future resolution at a between-versions query and is caught, a malformed date is rejected, and the ordering spot-check is correct; and the historical manifest resolver never returns a future manifest. Realtime not regressed (no deploy, live build b189d3cc0703 == T040). Cost (unknown != 0): production new_requests 0, D1 0, R2 0, model_calls 0. Ends IMPLEMENTATION_READY_FOR_INDEPENDENT_VERIFICATION.
